    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，feature_1放左边（order 0），main中间（order 1），feature_2右边（order 2）。另外需要显示分支线和提交标签。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "feature_1",
        "main",
        "feature_2",
        "showBranches",
        "showCommitLabel",
        "order"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，基础结构已设置。主干先有一个初始提交a，然后从main分出两个分支。feature_1先切过去做提交f，然后回main做提交b。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "commit a",
        "feature_1",
